The '''Council of Alwari Elders''' was a ruling body of the [[Alwari]] established in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]] after peace was brokered between the two major overclans, the [[Borokii]] and the [[Januul]]. It was formed from a union of the [[Januul Council of Elders]] and the [[Borokii Council of Elders]].<ref name="TAS">''[[The Approaching Storm]]''</ref>

